CERTIFICATE OF APPROVAL

 
 AMENDMENT No. III

I, Larry Morrin, Acting Area Director, Minneapolis Area Office, Bureau of Indian 
Affairs, by virtue of the authority granted to the Secretary of the Interior by the Act 
of June 18, 1934 (48 Stat. 984), as amended, which was delegated to me by 209 
DM, Secretary's Orders 3150 and 3177, and 10 BIAM Bulletin 13, as amended, do 
hereby approve the foregoing Amendment No. III to the Constitution of the Lower 
Sioux Indian Community. This amendment was duly adopted by a majority of the 
qualified voters who cast ballots in the November 17, 1998 election.

